            <div class="bg-primary-darker text-white radius-top-md">
                <h2 class="margin-0 padding-3">Terms and conditions</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body padding-3 font-sans-md line-height-sans-5">
                VA systems are intended to be used by authorized VA network users for viewing and retrieving information; 
                except as otherwise authorized for official business and limited personal use under VA policy. Information from 
                this system resides on and transmits through computer systems and networks funded by VA. Access or use 
                constitutes understanding and acceptance that there is no reasonable expectation of privacy in the use of 
                Government networks or systems. Access or use of this system constitutes user understanding and acceptance of 
                these terms and constitutes unconditional consent to review and action includes but is not limited to: monitoring; 
                recording; copying; auditing; inspecting;
            </div>
            <div class="padding-x-3 text-right">
                <%= form_tag({action: 'accept_terms', controller: 'users'}, method: :post) do |f| %>
                    <%= submit_tag 'I acknowledge the terms', class: 'usa-button margin-0 padding-2 margin-bottom-4 ' %>
                <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>